Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.54,0:04:03.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'm talking...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:06.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你无视她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}about you ignoring her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.03,0:04:13.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她有新号码给我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}She has a new number for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.71,0:04:21.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么拿到的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}How did you get this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.84,0:04:25.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在跟机器联络\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Are you communicating with the machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.19,0:04:28.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我理解你为什么不想干了  哈罗德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I understand why you want to quit, Harold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.90,0:04:30.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但现在不是时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}But now is not the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.89,0:04:32.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她要我们合作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}She wants us to work together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.43,0:04:50.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你有事瞒着我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I knew you were holding out on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.11,0:04:52.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你非要如此吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Must you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.91,0:04:54.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有新号码了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}So we have another number.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.46,0:04:57.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我还没决定  -决定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}- I haven't decided. - Decided?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.18,0:04:59.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为不需要你决定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I didn't think you got to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.85,0:05:01.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上  需要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Actually, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.79,0:05:07.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  那是马上要有决定了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Okay, well, is that going to happen anytime soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.63,0:05:10.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是要我先去别处找活儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}or should I be looking for some action elsewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.58,0:05:21.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟・克雷普\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Arthur Claypool.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.37,0:05:27.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有问题吗  芬奇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Something wrong, Finch?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.56,0:05:29.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  没事  我们该工作了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}No, nothing. We should get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.47,0:05:38.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在医院员工数据库里的身份是安・摩尔医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You're in the hospital's employee database as Dr. Anne Moore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.76,0:05:40.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你确定不想扮下医生吗  哈罗德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You sure you don't want to play M.D., Harold?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.00,0:05:42.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没当过令人信赖的医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I never made a convincing doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.44,0:05:43.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包括我当医生的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Even when I was one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.65,0:05:44.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我想我最好还是留在这儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}No, I think it's best if I stay here
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.98,0:05:47.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽可能地调查克雷普\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and find out as much as possible about Claypool.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.33,0:05:49.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那这家伙什么情况\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}So what are the details on this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.02,0:05:51.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他工作生活都在马里兰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He lives and works in Maryland.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.13,0:05:54.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到最近  他一直是家软件公司的IT顾问\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Until recently, he was an I.T. consultant at a software company,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.93,0:05:57.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁尼恩技术解决公司\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Runyon Technology Solutions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.74,0:05:59.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他最近的信用卡支出\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}His most recent credit card charges
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.66,0:06:01.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是医院的礼品店\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}are at the hospital gift shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.23,0:06:03.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在哪个房间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}What room's he in?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.09,0:06:03.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是古怪之处\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}That's the strange part.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.97,0:06:04.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找不到他在医院\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}There's no record of him
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.90,0:06:07.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住院部信息的记录\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}in the hospital's admissions system.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.58,0:06:10.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找到他了  他在这儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I got him. He's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.23,0:06:13.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那他的医疗记录肯定存档了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Then his medical records must be on file.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.71,0:06:15.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I found them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.83,0:06:19.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上边的确诊结果是多形性成胶质细胞瘤\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}According to this, his diagnosis is glioblastoma multiforme.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.18,0:06:23.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脑瘤  有病情预断吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Brain tumor. Does it give a prognosis?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.47,0:06:25.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚期\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Terminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.05,0:06:28.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要说这家伙是受害人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}So, assuming this guy is the victim,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.60,0:06:30.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁会要杀个将死之人呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}who would want to kill a dying man?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:32.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想这就需要我们来查了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I suppose that's what we need to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.34,0:06:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你今天怎么样  克雷普先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And how are you doing today, Mr. Claypool?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.01,0:06:49.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得是蜜蜂而非蜻蜓\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I suspect more honeybee than dragonfly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.40,0:06:51.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.26,0:06:52.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生命周期\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Lifespans.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.40,0:06:54.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜻蜓四个月  蜜蜂四周\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Dragonfly is four months. Honeybee is four weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:57.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要别是蜉蝣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}So long as you don't go mayfly on me,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.74,0:06:59.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就没问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}we won't have a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.39,0:07:00.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是新来的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Are you new?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.35,0:07:01.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是我又忘记你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Or have I just forgotten you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.08,0:07:03.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还没忘记我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You haven't forgotten me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.66,0:07:05.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迟早的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Give it time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.68,0:07:08.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的脑子  像是文件系统损坏的电脑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}My mind, it's like a computer with a corrupted file system.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.80,0:07:10.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想记起某件事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I know I want to remember something,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.46,0:07:12.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去打开文件时  文件却已经损坏了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and I go to open the file, and then it's just gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.63,0:07:13.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后突然间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And then, the next thing I know,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.89,0:07:15.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记忆如洪水般\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}memories come flooding back
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.36,0:07:18.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疯狂涌出\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and out of me like a loon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.12,0:07:20.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包括一些不该涌出的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Including a few that really shouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.22,0:07:22.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那又是些什么记忆呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And what memories are those?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.90,0:07:27.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克雷普先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Mr. Claypool?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.72,0:07:29.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给核心数据做了硬编码吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Have you hard-coded the essential values?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.00,0:07:30.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'm sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.73,0:07:34.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每次操作完都必须检查数据库\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We must check the database after every operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:35.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰一下  这位医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Excuse me, Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.16,0:07:39.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摩尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Moore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.07,0:07:40.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没在这层楼见过你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I haven't seen you on this floor before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.44,0:07:42.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我之前不在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}That's because I haven't been here before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.10,0:07:44.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我刚调过来  -从哪儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}- I just transferred in. - From where?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.25,0:07:45.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纽约综合医院\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}New York General.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.95,0:07:46.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什么科的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}What's your specialty?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.77,0:07:48.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,临床肿瘤和临终关怀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Clinical Oncology and Palliative Care.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.51,0:07:49.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}What's yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.53,0:07:53.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有任何需要就说一声\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Let me know if you need anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.11,0:07:54.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.87,0:08:03.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芬奇  有政府安保人员在保护克雷普\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Finch, Claypool has a government security detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.09,0:08:04.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说他是做什么工作来着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}What did you say his job was?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.60,0:08:07.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,IT顾问  这头衔很模糊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I.T. Consultant. I realize that's somewhat vague.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.17,0:08:09.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马里兰的地址  模糊的工作头衔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}A Maryland address, vague job title,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:10.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安保人员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}security detail--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.71,0:08:12.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看他有绝密权限甚至更高\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'd say he's got top-secret clearance or better.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.83,0:08:15.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说肿瘤让他的记忆如洪水般涌出\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He said his tumor was causing memories to flood out of him,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.54,0:08:17.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包括一些不该涌出的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}including some that shouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.25,0:08:18.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有可能是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Could be...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.54,0:08:21.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人策划将他灭口\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}someone's planning on shutting him up for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.51,0:08:29.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的安保人员用的是三人楔形站位\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}His security detail is using a three-man wedge formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.47,0:08:30.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说明什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Meaning what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.69,0:08:32.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说明他们是特勤局的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Meaning they're Secret Service.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.41,0:08:34.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芬奇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Finch...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.36,0:08:36.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙到底是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}who the hell is this guy?
