Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.60,0:13:42.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这倒是回答了刚才的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}That seems to answer the question
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.60,0:13:44.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克雷普是否为政府工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}of whether Claypool worked for the government.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.77,0:13:47.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  什么"撒马利亚人"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Yeah, on something called Samaritan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.63,0:13:49.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着耳熟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}The name is familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.01,0:13:51.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去查查\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'll see what I can dig up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.66,0:13:55.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看短时间内我无法接近克雷普了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I don't think I'll be getting close to Claypool anytime soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.23,0:13:58.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我可以接近第二选择\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}But I can get to the next best thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.10,0:14:11.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不是星巴克  但也凑和\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It's no Starbucks, but it gets the job done.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.52,0:14:14.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒没注意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I hadn't really noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.78,0:14:18.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉之前的闹剧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'm-- I'm sorry about the scene back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.85,0:14:22.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早就习惯了  这小意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Compared to what I'm used to, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.66,0:14:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道你怎么适应的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I don't know how you do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.66,0:14:26.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我讨厌医院\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Me, I hate hospitals.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.46,0:14:29.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可我现在得天天在这儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And now it seems it's where I spend all my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:32.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他什么时候确诊的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}When was he diagnosed?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.08,0:14:34.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大约一年前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}About a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:36.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,症状很明显\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}The signs were all there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.46,0:14:40.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是视而不见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I just didn't want to see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.66,0:14:43.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他经常在家附近迷路\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He was getting lost in the neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.74,0:14:49.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,性情大变\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He had a change in his temperament.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.81,0:14:54.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克雷普夫人  你知道有谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Mrs. Claypool, do you know of anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.46,0:14:56.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要伤害你丈夫吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}who'd want to hurt your husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.27,0:14:57.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Arthur?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.16,0:14:59.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.57,0:15:03.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是  现在也是  最温柔的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He was-- is the most gentle man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.94,0:15:05.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问这个干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Why would you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.47,0:15:06.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的安保\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}His security detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.82,0:15:08.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们啊  不是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Them. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.36,0:15:11.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为他的工作场所\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}They're just here because of where he worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.47,0:15:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And where was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.34,0:15:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国家安全局\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}The National Security Agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.90,0:15:19.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他肯定不想我告诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He would not want me to tell you that,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.25,0:15:22.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我认为已经没有隐瞒的必要了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}but I don't really see the point in hiding it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.89,0:15:26.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你丈夫肯定很重要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Your husband must be a pretty important guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.27,0:15:28.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I wouldn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.74,0:15:32.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作的事他从来不和我说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He never talked to me about his work,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.42,0:15:35.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后来我也不问了  然后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}So I finally just stopped asking, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.78,0:15:39.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们慢慢连话都不说了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}we kind of stopped talking altogether.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.06,0:15:42.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说话本来就没用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Talking's overrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.66,0:15:48.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说  那肯定不好受\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I mean, that must have been really hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.06,0:15:50.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正不好受的是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Not as hard as realizing the person you spent
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.99,0:15:52.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟你共度半生的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}half your life with
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.14,0:15:54.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不记得你是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}doesn't even know who you are anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.85,0:15:59.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许因为这个  我才总来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And I suppose that's why I keep coming back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.47,0:16:03.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望亚瑟能记起我是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Just on the hope that Arthur will remember who I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.77,0:16:05.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕只有一瞬间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}even for a moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.74,0:16:07.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他想起来的时候  我一定要在他身边\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and if he does, I'm going to be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.71,0:16:10.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.54,0:16:14.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我  该回去工作了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I...should get back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.58,0:16:22.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的安保人员撤了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}His security detail is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.85,0:16:24.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那克雷普呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And Claypool?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.66,0:16:35.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.60,0:16:37.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个房间的病人呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Where is the patient that was assigned to this room?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.38,0:16:39.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他去造影了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He was taken to radiology.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.33,0:16:48.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芬奇  克雷普的妻子说他是国安局的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Finch, Claypool's wife said he was N.S.A.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.77,0:16:49.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就对了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}That fits.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.91,0:16:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道我听说过"撒马利亚人"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I knew I'd heard Samaritan before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.52,0:16:53.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是国安局机密项目\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It was a classified N.S.A. project.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.68,0:16:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2005年被国会停止资助并关闭了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Congress de-funded and then shut it down in 2005,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.88,0:16:59.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是克雷普现在记忆中的时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}which is clearly the time Claypool is living in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.67,0:17:01.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然克雷普曾就职于国安局\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}If Claypool was career N.S.A.,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.38,0:17:04.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那他肯定接触过各种绝密情报\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}then he'd be read in on all sorts of top-secret information.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.10,0:17:06.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他现在一嚷嚷别人就知道了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Information he's now shouting for anyone to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.12,0:17:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能想到十五家国外情报机构\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I can think of about 15 foreign intelligence agencies
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.99,0:17:12.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会拼命想得到这些情报\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}that would kill for that intel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.94,0:17:14.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想也是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}That occurred to me as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.61,0:17:17.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且威胁可能就来自\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}As did the possibility that the threat may be
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.25,0:17:19.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他自己的安保人员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}from his own security detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.68,0:17:21.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了保护政府的秘密\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}To protect the government's secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.73,0:17:23.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得接近他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You need to get close to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.27,0:17:26.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来容易做起来难\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Easier said than done.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.47,0:17:49.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  我进来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Okay, I'm in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.50,0:17:50.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心点  肖女士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Be careful, Ms. Shaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.56,0:17:52.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没有支援给你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I have no backup that I can send you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.84,0:17:54.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我快点儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Then, I'll be quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.40,0:17:59.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-放松  克雷普先生  -等等\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}- Relax, Mr. Claypool. - Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.18,0:18:03.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,垃圾桶里有个注射器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}A syringe in the trashcan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.07,0:18:03.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克雷普在造影前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Claypool would have been injected
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.97,0:18:06.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能被注射了放射性示踪剂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}with a radio tracer prior to his scan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.19,0:18:10.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是硫喷妥钠[吐真剂]\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It's sodium pentothol.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.81,0:18:14.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东西在谁手里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Who has them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.11,0:18:15.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁迪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Rudy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.53,0:18:16.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁迪在哪儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And where is Rudy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.98,0:18:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是造影  而是审问\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}This isn't a scan. It's an interrogation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.69,0:18:24.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切还好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Is everything all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.13,0:18:26.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.40,0:18:27.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威胁克雷普的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Whoever the threat against Claypool is,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.51,0:18:28.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}they're already here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.34,0:18:31.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住  别动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Freeze! Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.56,0:18:33.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肖女士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Ms. Shaw?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.37,0:18:36.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就"快"成这样了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}So much for being quick.
