Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.70,0:19:00.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在造什么  儿子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}What you building there, son?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.19,0:19:02.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是浮栅晶体管列阵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It's an array of floating gate transistors,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.20,0:19:04.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,配置成"与非"门\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}configured as a series of N.A.N.D. gates.
