Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.22,0:29:25.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估计那些对我们开枪的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I expect the people shooting at us
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.52,0:29:26.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}knew that as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.65,0:29:27.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们不是要杀你  亚瑟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}They're not trying to kill you, Arthur,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.98,0:29:30.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少拿到他们想要的情报之前不会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}at least not until they get some information out of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.36,0:29:31.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么情报\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}What information?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.24,0:29:32.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你之前在医院做扫描的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}When you were being scanned at the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.58,0:29:34.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那造影师问你  东西在谁手里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}the technician asked you who had them.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.93,0:29:38.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-东西  -你回答  "鲁迪"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}- Them. - And you answered, "Rudy."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.11,0:29:40.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.47,0:29:41.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Who were you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.70,0:29:45.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道  抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I don't know. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.88,0:29:48.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系  不如休息下吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}That's all right. Why don't you rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.98,0:29:49.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈罗德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Harold...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.65,0:29:52.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟这些事有什么关系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}what do you have to do with all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.16,0:29:55.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是听说你可能有麻烦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I just heard that you might be in some trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.22,0:29:56.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来  坐下吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Come on, let's get you settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.00,0:30:03.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不该离窗户这么近\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You really shouldn't stand so close to the windows.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.73,0:30:06.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Who are you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.49,0:30:09.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护你和你丈夫安全的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We're the ones keeping you and your husband safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.81,0:30:11.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的安保人员呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}What about his security detail?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.42,0:30:13.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是该让特勤局知道我们在这儿吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Shouldn't the Secret Service know we're here?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.67,0:30:15.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在  我唯一相信的人都在屋子里了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Right now, the only people I trust are in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.50,0:30:40.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你感觉好点了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You feeling better?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.89,0:30:42.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈罗德   你还记得 \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Harold, do you recall
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.87,0:30:45.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,《崛起麻省理工仔》吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Arise, ye sons of M.I.T.?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.59,0:30:46.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I--
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.19,0:30:50.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,崛起麻省理工仔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Arise, ye sons of M.I.T.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.53,0:30:53.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,荣耀归我兄弟会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}In loyal brotherhood
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.75,0:30:56.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天生我才必有用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}The future beckons unto ye
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.06,0:30:59.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白日放歌需纵酒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And life is full and good
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.40,0:31:02.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,崛起崛起再崛起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Arise, and raise
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.02,0:31:04.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人生得意需尽欢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Your steins on high
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.25,0:31:07.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今宵酒醒何处\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Tonight shall ever be
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.76,0:31:11.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是夜永铭于心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}A memory that will never die
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.07,0:31:15.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻省理工仔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Ye sons of M.I.T.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.78,0:31:19.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约翰要后悔错过这一幕了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}John's gonna be sorry he missed that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.86,0:31:21.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Now, Arthur,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.16,0:31:23.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"撒马利亚人"是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}What was Samaritan?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.67,0:31:31.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.20,0:31:35.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"撒马利亚人"是非凡的项目\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Samaritan is truly a remarkable project.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.62,0:31:37.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么非凡  说说看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You say it is remarkable. Tell me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.14,0:31:41.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它的主要功能是通过分析大型数据集\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Its primary function is to detect potential acts of terror
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.31,0:31:43.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,检测出潜在的恐怖活动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}through analysis of large data sets.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.03,0:31:45.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,具体说来  它的能力是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Specifically, it will have the ability
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.01,0:31:47.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预见行凶者的侵害行动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}to anticipate acts of aggression
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.79,0:31:50.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并提出相应的战略对策\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and suggest strategic countermeasures
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.57,0:31:52.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,制止其付诸行动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}before the perpetrators can act.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.99,0:31:56.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这项目听起来很厉害\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It sounds like quite a project.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.90,0:31:58.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"撒马利亚人"是革命性的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Samaritan is revolutionary.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.24,0:32:01.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不只是因为它能做什么  而是它如何做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Not so much for what it does, but how it does it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.95,0:32:04.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我将系统设计成自主控制\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}The system was designed to function autonomously,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.60,0:32:07.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能通过分析过去运行经验\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}to continually adapt and upgrade itself
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.70,0:32:09.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自动改写与升级\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}through past experiences.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.20,0:32:12.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说它能记忆和学习\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You're saying that it can remember and learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.50,0:32:14.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.16,0:32:15.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈罗德  这是我们一直以来的梦想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Harold, it's what we always dreamed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.98,0:32:18.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"撒马利亚人"是真正的人工智能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Samaritan is a true artificial intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.21,0:32:20.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得对  亚瑟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You're right, Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.78,0:32:22.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确非凡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}That is remarkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.87,0:32:23.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失陪一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.99,0:32:31.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说的  是我想的那个吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Is he talking about what I think he's talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.69,0:32:32.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It would appear so.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.19,0:32:36.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那就意味着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}But then that would mean--
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.76,0:32:38.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有第二台机器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}That there was a second machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.05,0:32:41.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟造的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And Arthur built it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.48,0:32:51.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Copy that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.51,0:32:53.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到哈罗德了  现在带他俩回家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I found Harold, and I'm taking them both home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.70,0:32:54.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\fn微软雅黑\c&H000000&\fs11\b1\frz-0.5\pos(194.144,56.455)}获取爱荷华公共安全记录
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.70,0:32:54.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\fn微软雅黑\c&HFFFFFF&\fs11\b1\frz-0.5\pos(255.388,71.182)}日期: 1979年11月4日
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.70,0:32:54.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\fn微软雅黑\c&HFFFFFF&\fs12\b1\pos(254.163,100.636)}分局: 爱荷华巡警11局
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.70,0:32:54.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\fn微软雅黑\c&HFFFFFF&\fs11\b1\pos(256,115.364)}地点: 爱荷华州拉西特
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.70,0:32:54.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\fn微软雅黑\c&HFFFFFF&\fs12\b1\pos(214.354,145.636)}事件类型: 公民需要帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.51,0:32:54.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Ten-four.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.70,0:33:20.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子  他今晚在离家不到一公里处迷路了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Son, he wandered half a mile away from home tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.27,0:33:23.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果气温降到零下怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}What happens when it drops below zero?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.98,0:33:25.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你心有余而力不足\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}If you're stretched past the point
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.34,0:33:26.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给不了他需要的帮助\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}where you can give him what he needs,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.98,0:33:29.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许该给他找个能帮助他的地方了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}maybe it's time to find a place that can.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.08,0:33:39.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'm sorry, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.32,0:33:43.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道为什么总是这样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I don't know why this keeps happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.13,0:33:46.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总是忘记别人  忘记自己身在何处\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I forget who people are, where I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.19,0:33:47.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的  爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It's okay, dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.18,0:33:49.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  有关系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.18,0:33:53.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你拥有了不起的能力  哈罗德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You have greatness in you, Harold.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.76,0:33:55.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的头脑  你的预见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Your mind, the things that you can see--
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.81,0:33:56.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是  爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It's not-- dad--
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.84,0:33:58.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这儿太浪费了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And it's wasted here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.73,0:34:00.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该去上大学\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You should be heading off to college,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.53,0:34:02.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而不是照顾个老头子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}not taking care of an old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.19,0:34:04.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会离开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'm not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.01,0:34:08.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说  他们正在造一个电脑网络\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And besides, they're building a computer network right now
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.46,0:34:11.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够把国内所有的大学都联网\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}that's going to connect all the universities in the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.54,0:34:13.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然我不能离开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}If I can't leave town,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.00,0:34:16.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就把信息都弄过来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'll bring the information to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.55,0:34:17.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会有办法的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'll find a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.42,0:34:23.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心  儿子  别太鲁莽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Careful, son. Don't be reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.57,0:34:25.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别进你不该进的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Don't get yourself into something you shouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.35,0:34:27.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他们不想被人进去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}If they don't want you to get inside,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.65,0:34:30.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就应该造好点儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}they ought to build it better.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.81,0:34:34.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.66,0:34:41.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你造的机器  亚瑟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}This machine you built, Arthur...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.33,0:34:44.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"撒马利亚人"  它现在在哪儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Samaritan-- where is it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.58,0:34:45.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没在哪儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.37,0:34:47.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"撒马利亚人"数年前被毁了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Samaritan was destroyed years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.99,0:34:49.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2005年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}2005.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.74,0:34:52.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毁了  为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Destroyed? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.41,0:34:54.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,911之后  政府发动所有的力量\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}After 9/11, the government had everyone and their cat
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.72,0:34:56.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想造一个监视一切的系统\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}trying to build a system that could watch everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.85,0:34:58.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们也找上你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}They came to you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.20,0:35:00.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  我告诉他们  要想如愿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Yes. I told them the only way they could achieve what they wanted
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.70,0:35:02.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所造的系统要不仅能监视一切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}was to build something that not only watched,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.41,0:35:05.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要能理解\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}but understood what it was watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.76,0:35:07.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人工智能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}An A.I.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.87,0:35:11.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你总说人工智能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I know you always said artificial intelligence
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.07,0:35:13.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能  哈罗德  但是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}was a fool's errand, Harold, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.26,0:35:16.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我几乎成功了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I was this close.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.93,0:35:17.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,几乎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Close?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.92,0:35:20.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让"撒马利亚人"成功上线\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}To making Samaritan operational.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.68,0:35:23.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实上  我没能运行起来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Truth is, I couldn't get it to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.04,0:35:25.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本来可以的  只要那些没脑子的官僚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I mean, I could've, if those pinhead bureaucrats
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.74,0:35:27.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再多给我几周的时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}would have just given me a few more weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.36,0:35:28.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道我能成功的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I know I could have cracked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.57,0:35:30.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国会就在那时叫停了你们的项目\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And that's when congress shut you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.15,0:35:32.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不止是我们  是所有的项目\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Not just us. All the programs.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.52,0:35:34.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星风  海浪  创世纪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Stellar Wind, Tides, Genysis,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.22,0:35:37.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未来地图  热那亚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Futuremap, Genoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.21,0:35:39.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六个月内  全都没了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Within six months, they were all gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.80,0:35:43.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们2005年2月25日对"撒马利亚人"下了手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}They came for Samaritan February 25, 2005.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.26,0:35:49.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是为避免"侵犯公民自由"什么的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}For fear of "violating civil liberties," or so they said.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.95,0:35:52.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你认为另有原因\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And you thought there was another reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.97,0:35:54.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,政府想要一个系统  哈罗德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}The government wanted a system, Harold.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.68,0:35:56.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们不会轻易放弃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}They weren't just going to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.51,0:35:58.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们让国会把我们全叫停\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}They let congress shut us down,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.20,0:35:59.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只留下了"棱镜"那破玩意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}all except for that piece of crap Prism,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.96,0:36:02.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那只是掩人耳目\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}but that was just to throw anyone off the scent.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.62,0:36:03.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.01,0:36:05.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们已经建成了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}They'd already found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.49,0:36:07.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人捷足先登了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Someone else had got there first.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.34,0:36:10.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,造出了它\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And built it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.03,0:36:20.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说"喝酒"  苏打水可不算\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}When I said "drink", I didn't mean club soda.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.53,0:36:25.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芬奇还指派你当我的代驾司机吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Finch appoint you to be my designated driver too?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.32,0:36:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  聪明小子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}No, smart guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.04,0:36:30.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我戒酒两年了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'm two years sober.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.03,0:36:33.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.14,0:36:35.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那时我做了不少蠢事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Because back when I was doing a lot of stupid things,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.87,0:36:37.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酗酒也是其中之一\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}drinking was one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.17,0:36:41.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后有个西装混蛋出现在我的后座\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And then this jackass in a suit showed up on my backseat
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.26,0:36:45.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿枪逼着我帮他  让我审视自己\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and forced me at gunpoint to help him and take a look at who I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.42,0:36:47.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我戒酒的原因\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Why'd I quit drinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.27,0:36:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.12,0:36:51.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可别得意洋洋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Don't let it go to your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.61,0:36:54.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来一杯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Another.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.74,0:36:57.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为呢  就你一个人痛苦吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}What do you think, you're the only one that's hurting?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.73,0:36:59.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我搭档被枪杀了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}My partner got shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.01,0:37:00.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我难道躲在你老爸过去的酒吧里买醉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}So tell me how hiding out in your old man's watering hole
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.60,0:37:02.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能修补好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}is gonna fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.05,0:37:13.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在八公里开外看到个军事基地的标志\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I saw the sign for the army base about five miles back.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.68,0:37:16.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本以为这儿可能是你以前的驻地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I thought maybe this was where you were stationed.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.95,0:37:18.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到我看到这张照片\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Until I saw the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.63,0:37:20.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那相似度\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And the resemblance.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.87,0:37:26.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爸被派去越南前就驻扎在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}My dad was here before he was deployed to Vietnam.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.51,0:37:28.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,服了四期兵役\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Did four tours.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.88,0:37:32.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是真正的战争英雄\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He was a bona fide war hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.05,0:37:34.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他是阵亡的吗  -不是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}- Was he killed in action? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.20,0:37:37.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在他工作的冶炼厂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}At the refinery where he worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.72,0:37:40.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回家还不过两个月\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Hadn't even been home two months.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.88,0:37:42.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是难接受\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}That's rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.59,0:37:44.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这和卡特的事有什么关系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}But what's that have to do with what happened to Carter?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.94,0:37:46.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.66,0:37:50.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是证明了在这个世界上无论我们怎么做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Just proves that no matter what we do or don't do in this world,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.57,0:37:52.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该出事还是会出事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}bad things are still gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.62,0:37:53.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.82,0:37:56.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毫无意义\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.13,0:38:00.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无关紧要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.60,0:38:01.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么能这么说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}How can you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.47,0:38:05.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你救了很多人  包括我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You saved lots of people, including me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.53,0:38:07.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说这毫无意义吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You're saying that was pointless?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.20,0:38:12.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.10,0:38:14.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.83,0:38:17.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'm not leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.80,0:38:22.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没说要离开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I wasn't talking about leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.67,0:38:33.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会和你打架的  莱奈尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'm not gonna fight you, Lionel.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.24,0:38:43.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.60,0:38:50.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.82,0:39:14.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.70,0:39:41.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  应该可以了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Okay, that should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.46,0:39:44.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天此时  亚瑟・克雷普和黛安・克雷普\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}This time tomorrow, Arthur and Diane Claypool
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.33,0:39:46.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是亨利・麦卡锡和伊莱恩・麦卡锡了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}will be Henry and Elaine Mccarthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.72,0:39:50.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在多伦多医院给亚瑟安排了病房\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I've also arranged a room for Arthur at a Toronto hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.49,0:39:51.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们明天一早就离开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We'll leave first thing in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.96,0:39:53.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果还有需要我的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}If there's anything I can do--
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.35,0:39:54.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.40,0:39:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  我只是想和他谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'm sorry, I was just trying to talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.16,0:39:59.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.88,0:40:01.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能别再烦我了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Why don't you just leave me alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.15,0:40:02.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-亚瑟  没事的  -不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}- Arthur, it's okay. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.88,0:40:04.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能把我困在这儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And you can't keep me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.16,0:40:06.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真相无惧质疑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}The truth fears no questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.69,0:40:09.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟  是我  哈罗德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Arthur, it's me, Harold.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.47,0:40:11.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈罗德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Harold?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.11,0:40:14.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是黛安  你的妻子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And this is Diane, your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.16,0:40:19.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么会只记得你  不记得她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}How come I remember you and not her?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.57,0:40:22.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为肿瘤影响了你的记忆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Because tumors do mysterious things to memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.43,0:40:24.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不  -正如你所说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}- No. - It's like you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.16,0:40:25.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的文件系统损坏了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Your file system is corrupted.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.87,0:40:28.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}No. That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.57,0:40:31.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得黛安\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I remember Diane.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.87,0:40:36.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黛安死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Diane is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.73,0:40:38.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我两年前埋葬了她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I buried her two years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.02,0:40:39.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在2011年6月12日\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}on June 12, 2011.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.04,0:40:44.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的记得\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You do remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.01,0:40:46.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.19,0:40:58.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来这是不可避免了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I suppose this was inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.33,0:41:03.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逝去的时光是多么奢侈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And seeing as how time is a luxury we no longer have--
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.12,0:41:09.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赫什\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Hersh.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.16,0:41:12.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周边安全  夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Perimeter is secure, Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.04,0:41:16.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.75,0:41:18.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是你的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He works for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.80,0:41:22.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你曾经也是  肖探员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}As did you at one time, Agent Shaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.21,0:41:26.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜你一直想见我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I assume you always wanted to meet me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.56,0:41:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主控者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Control.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.44,0:41:30.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本来还担心你会影响\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I was concerned that you might disrupt
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.54,0:41:32.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我接近亚瑟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}my attempts to get close to Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.45,0:41:37.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  你真是相当有用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}However, you proved to be quite useful,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.24,0:41:40.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那些误入歧途的隐私恐怖分子手里救了他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}saving him from those misguided privacy terrorists
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.18,0:41:44.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还安排我见到了你的雇主\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and arranging it so I could meet your employer,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.16,0:41:46.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是久仰了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}who I've heard so much about.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.26,0:41:50.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.74,0:41:53.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还不知道你姓什么呢  哈罗德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I didn't catch your last name, Harold.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.56,0:41:55.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想从亚瑟那儿知道什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}What is it that you want from Arthur?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.30,0:41:56.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是情报罢了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Just information.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.99,0:41:59.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他最伟大的成就下落何在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}The location of his greatest achievement,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.52,0:42:01.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"撒马利亚人"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Samaritan.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.68,0:42:04.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撒马  不  "撒马利亚人"被毁了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Samar--no. Samaritan was destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.04,0:42:07.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道官方说法  亚瑟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I know the official story, Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.00,0:42:10.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还知道硬盘的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I also know about the drives.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.69,0:42:17.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东西在哪儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.70,0:42:19.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道你在说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.48,0:42:21.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  够了  他说的是事实\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}All right, stop it. He's telling you the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.08,0:42:22.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He doesn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.34,0:42:24.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很快会查明的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'll find out soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.31,0:42:27.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然我们有幸见面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And since you and I have had the good fortune of meeting,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.61,0:42:29.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以帮我拿回另一件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}you can help me recover something else
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.14,0:42:30.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,属于我的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}that belongs to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.10,0:42:33.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最伟大的成就\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Your greatest achievement.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.30,0:42:35.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕不行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'm afraid I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.37,0:42:39.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们中会有人开口告诉我我想知道的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}One of you is going to tell me what it is I want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.09,0:42:41.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开口的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And whoever does...
